title: Corsairs - Conquest at sea
description:
Corsairs - Conquest at sea


Control the actions of up to 30 of your men in real time. You sail off to conquer the new world! Overcome hoards of Pirates! Improve buildings such as the lighthouse to see enemies further away. With different missions during which you sail around the Caribbean, the Madagascar region, along the coast of Asia until you finally reach Australia. You will build and control an entire armada, fight in unfriendly seas, win over new trading posts, negotiate with new territories for personal enrichment, foil the plans of other nations, and overcome the hoards of pirates sailing the seas. You will meet infamous people through battles or because of their cruelty (such as Surcouf or the terrifying Blackbeard).


Pls seed.
